----------------
ActivityJob Used
----------------
*bank = created, updated, destroyed
booking - accpeted, cancelled, denied, finished, requested, 
charge - created
customer - created, destroyed, updated
license - uploaded
payout - cancelled, failed, paid, processing
photo - created, updated
provider - activated, created, disabled, pending, unverified, verified
review - created

---------------
NotificationJob
---------------
booking - accpeted, cancelled, denied, finished, requested
card - created, deleted
*card = created, destroyed, updated
charge - created
promo - created, redeemed
refund - created
review - created, updated
user - created, destroyed

